LibraryServiceClient
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

.. code:: py

    from google.cloud.example import library_v1

    client = library_v1.LibraryServiceClient()

    name = client.book_path('[SHELF_ID]', '[BOOK_ID]')
    book = {}

    response = client.update_book(name, book)

